document_data.name: Balinaikal
document_data.mainbody: '''Balinaikal''' was an [[ogre mage]] who ruled the [[Palace of Balinaikal]] in the [[Northern Wastes]] of [[Kara-Tur]]. He was supremely powerful, and killed or enslaved all who trespassed upon his domain.
